 2. You are returning the values and in else part returning `0` .That is why you are having 0 in your result . 
  Instead of returning the existing value return only `true` or `false` that way it will be much easier to control and organized.

```
    private static boolean hasSquare(Integer i, List&lt;Integer&gt; list) {
